{"data":[{"name":"82:1","price":"1. Als de hemel splijt.","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنفَطَرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5830,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:2","price":"2. En als de sterren gevallen en verspreid zijn.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡكَوَاكِبُ ٱنتَثَرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5831,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:3","price":"3. En als de zeeën overstromen.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡبِحَارُ فُجِّرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5832,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:4","price":"4. En als de graven zich omkeren.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡقُبُورُ بُعۡثِرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5833,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:5","price":"5. (Dan) zal men weten wat hij voortgebracht heeft en wat hij achter zich heeft gelaten (door goede of slechte daden).","arabic":"عَلِمَتۡ نَفۡسٞ مَّا قَدَّمَتۡ وَأَخَّرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5834,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:6","price":"6. O mens! Wat heeft jou onachtzaam gemaakt over jullie Heer, de meest Edele.","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا غَرَّكَ بِرَبِّكَ ٱلۡكَرِيمِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5835,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:7","price":"7. Die jullie geschapen heeft, jullie perfect heeft gevormd en de juiste verhoudingen heeft gegeven.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَكَ فَسَوَّىٰكَ فَعَدَلَكَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5836,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:8","price":"8. In welke vorm Hij ook wilde, heeft Hij jullie samengesteld.","arabic":"فِيٓ أَيِّ صُورَةٖ مَّا شَآءَ رَكَّبَكَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5837,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:9","price":"9. Welnee! Maar jullie ontkennen de vergelding.","arabic":"كَلَّا بَلۡ تُكَذِّبُونَ بِٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5838,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:10","price":"10. Maar waarlijk, over jullie staan wakers (engelen) ,die over jullie waken (als jullie waken over jullie Tawhied, Islam, geloof).","arabic":"وَإِنَّ عَلَيۡكُمۡ لَحَٰفِظِينَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5839,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:11","price":"11. Eervollen engelen schrijven jullie daden op.","arabic":"كِرَامٗا كَٰتِبِينَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5840,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:12","price":"12. Zij weten alles wat jullie doen.","arabic":"يَعۡلَمُونَ مَا تَفۡعَلُونَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5841,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:13","price":"13. Waarlijk de vromen en rechtvaardigen zullen in de verheerlijking (het paradijs) zijn.","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارَ لَفِي نَعِيمٖ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5842,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:14","price":"14. En waarlijk de zondaren (ongelovigen en misdadigers) zullen in het laaiend vuur (de hel) zijn.","arabic":"وَإِنَّ ٱلۡفُجَّارَ لَفِي جَحِيمٖ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5843,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:15","price":"15. Zij zullen binnen op de dag der vergelding.","arabic":"يَصۡلَوۡنَهَا يَوۡمَ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5844,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:16","price":"16. En zij (de zondaren) zullen daar niet weg kunnen gaan.","arabic":"وَمَا هُمۡ عَنۡهَا بِغَآئِبِينَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5845,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:17","price":"17. En wat doet jullie weten wat de dag van de vergelding is?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5846,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:18","price":"18. Nogmaals, wat doet jullie weten wat de dag van de vergelding is?","arabic":"ثُمَّ مَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5847,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"82:19","price":"19. (Het zal) de dag zijn waarop niemand de kracht heeft om iets voor een ander te doen, en alles hangt die dag geheel van Allah af.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ لَا تَمۡلِكُ نَفۡسٞ لِّنَفۡسٖ شَيۡـٔٗاۖ وَٱلۡأَمۡرُ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلَّهِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5848,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"}],"chapter":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar","Chapter Al-Infitar","Infitar","Surah Infitar","Chapter Infitar","Al Infitar","Surah Al Infitar","Chapter Al Infitar","Surah 82","Chapter 82","The Cleaving","الإنفطار"]}